    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，GAME和HAND_SUMMARY是一对多关系？还是严格的一对一？另外HAND_SUMMARY的主键用hand_number，那是否需要关联到具体的game_id作为外键？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GAME",
