      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是一对多，一个GAME包含多手。hand_number需要联合game_id才能唯一确定，不过我们让hand_number本身作为PK，然后用game_id做FK指向GAME。关系写成GAME包含HAND_SUMMARY。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GAME",
        "HAND_SUMMARY",
        "game_id",
        "hand_number",
        "includes"
